[SHORT DESC]
Has 1/4 recoil.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage, and the user receives recoil damage equal to 1/4 of the damage dealt, rounded half up, but not less than 1 HP.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Take Down has no competitive use. It is poorly distributed, has terrible accuracy, and is weaker than Return, which doesn't inflict recoil damage.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/return">Return</a> and <a href="/bw/moves/frustration">Frustration</a> are both more powerful alternatives that do not cause recoil damage.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/double-edge">Double-Edge</a> is a much more powerful move, which also deals recoil damage.</p>